   "source": [
    "Preprocessing includes:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Type conversion:** Parse `date_time` as timestamp.\n",
    "2. **Filtering:** Remove points outside the Beijing bounding box (lat 39.83-40.12, lon 116.25-116.64).\n",
    "3. **Missing data:** Drop null coordinate or timestamp rows.\n",
    "4. **Trajectory ID:** Assign a unique `trajectory\\_id` per trip.\n",
    "5. **Subsetting:** Create 5\\%, 10\\%, and 25\\% trajectory-level subsets using a fixed seed (42); retain the full dataset.\n",
    "\n",
    "Clustering uses cleaned data without feature engineering."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 0,
   "metadata": {
    "application/vnd.databricks.v1+cell": {
     "cellMetadata": {
      "byteLimit": 2048000,
